---
title: Orchestrator Push Pattern — orchestrator dispatches task, agent streams results
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant ORC as Orchestrator
    participant REDIS as Redis Streams
    participant CL as coverage-left<br/>(MCP Server)

    Note over ORC,CL: Precondition: entity-extractor STOP received.<br/>Parallel fan-out begins. Same pattern runs<br/>concurrently for coverage-center, coverage-right,<br/>domain-evidence.

    ORC->>CL: MCP invoke_task({<br/>  run_id: "claim-4821-run-003",<br/>  task: "analyze_left_coverage",<br/>  claim_text: "Biden issued...",<br/>  entities: [{type: "PERSON", value: "Biden"}, ...]<br/>})

    CL-->>ORC: MCP task_accepted({<br/>  run_id: "claim-4821-run-003",<br/>  agent: "coverage-left"<br/>})

    Note over CL: Agent queries NewsAPI and MBFC<br/>independently. No MCP calls back<br/>to orchestrator during execution.

    CL->>CL: query NewsAPI for left-spectrum<br/>sources covering claim entities

    CL->>CL: query MBFC for source<br/>bias ratings

    CL->>CL: reason over article set,<br/>determine framing and credibility

    CL->>REDIS: XADD reasoning:claim-4821-run-003:coverage-left *<br/>type=START phase=fanout

    CL->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(COVERAGE_ARTICLE_COUNT, 12, P)
    CL->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(COVERAGE_FRAMING, SUPPORTIVE, P)

    CL->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(COVERAGE_ARTICLE_COUNT, 12, F)
    CL->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(COVERAGE_FRAMING, SUPPORTIVE, F)
    CL->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(COVERAGE_TOP_SOURCE, "DailyKos", F)
    CL->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(COVERAGE_TOP_SOURCE_URL, "https://...", F)

    CL->>REDIS: XADD ... type=STOP<br/>finalStatus=F observationCount=6

    Note over ORC,REDIS: Orchestrator consumes via XREADGROUP.<br/>Receives START, all OBS, and STOP in order.<br/>Does not issue MCP calls to read agent state.

    ORC->>REDIS: XREADGROUP — consume STOP message

    ORC->>ORC: update completion register<br/>coverage-left = COMPLETE

    Note over ORC: Orchestrator waits for coverage-center,<br/>coverage-right, claimreview-matcher,<br/>domain-evidence STOP messages before<br/>dispatching blindspot-detector.
